al\">$cliente</font></td>";	     echo "<td width=\"35%\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">$servico</font></td>";	     echo "<td width=\"20%\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">$classe_cep</font></td>";	     echo "<td width=\"10%\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">$valor</font></td>";         echo "</tr>";       }?></table></div></BODY></HTML>